{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies/about","content_id":"2f93de59-1797-46ad-860d-6957e4427cab","description":"The Office for the Pay Review Bodies provides an independent secretariat to 8 Pay Review Bodies which make recommendations impacting 2.5 million workers – around 45% of public sector staff – and a pay bill of £100 billion. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We provide an independent secretariat to: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/armed-forces-pay-review-body\">Armed Forces’ Pay Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"Armed Forces' Pay Review Body \">AFPRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/review-body-on-doctors-and-dentists-remuneration\">Review Body on Doctors’ and Dentists’ Remuneration</a> (<abbr title=\"Review Body on Doctors' and Dentists' Remuneration \">DDRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nhs-pay-review-body\">NHS Pay Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"NHS Pay Review Body \">NHSPRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/prison-services-pay-review-body\">Prison Service Pay Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"Prison Service Pay Review Body \">PSPRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/school-teachers-review-body\">School Teachers’ Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"School Teachers' Review Body \">STRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/review-body-on-senior-salaries\">Senior Salaries Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"Senior Salaries Review Body \">SSRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/police-remuneration-review-body\">Police Remuneration Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"Police Remuneration Review Body \">PRRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/national-crime-agency-remuneration-review-body\">National Crime Agency Remuneration Review Body</a> (<abbr title=\"National Crime Agency Remuneration Review Body \">NCARRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Read an <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/pay-review-bodies-and-police-boards-introduction\">introduction to pay review bodies</a> </p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are </h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office for the Pay Review Bodies \">OPRB</abbr> is staffed by around 30 civil servants organised into: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>secretariat teams, which support each of the bodies by co-ordinating and managing research and consultancy projects </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>a Central Support Unit  </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Office for the Pay Review Bodies \">OPRB</abbr> senior management team includes: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>David Fry (<abbr title=\"Office for the Pay Review Bodies \">OPRB</abbr> Director) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Abbie Lloyd (<abbr title=\"NHS Pay Review Body \">NHSPRB</abbr>, <abbr title=\"Review Body on Doctors' and Dentists' Remuneration \">DDRB</abbr>, <abbr title=\"National Crime Agency Remuneration Review Body \">NCARRB</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Police Remuneration Review Body \">PRRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Robin Webb  (<abbr title=\"Senior Salaries Review Body \">SSRB</abbr>)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Caitriona Byrne and Jo Israel (Jobshare) (<abbr title=\"School Teachers' Review Body \">STRB</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Senior Salaries Review Body \">SSRB</abbr> Major Review of the Judicial Salary Structure)</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Mike Batley (Chief Economist, <abbr title=\"Armed Forces' Pay Review Body \">AFPRB</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Prison Service Pay Review Body \">PSPRB</abbr>) </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities </h2>\n\n<p>We are responsible for: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>obtaining timely, high quality evidence and providing research, analysis and advice to inform review bodies’ decisions and to underpin their recommendations </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>enabling the review bodies to deliver their reports to the timescale and process required and in accordance with their individual terms of reference and remits - in particular through providing high quality secretariat services and through managing relationships with all parties to the process </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>managing <abbr title=\"Office for the Pay Review Bodies \">OPRB</abbr> resources effectively with particular emphasis on flexible organisation and ways of working, project management and meeting any budgetary and/or headcount reductions agreed with <abbr title=\"Department for Business and Trade\">DBT</abbr>. </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"updated the senior management list","public_timestamp":"2025-02-27T13:22:59Z"},{"note":"updated the senior management list.","public_timestamp":"2025-02-27T11:59:08Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2024-10-03T11:21:11Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["2d413a29-41da-4fd2-a295-f40fc5cd751a"],"name":"Access our information"}],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are "},{"id":"responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Responsibilities "}],"organisation":"41850af4-7abb-434a-b11a-13263b58afe7","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2024-10-03T12:21:11+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies/about","content_id":"2f93de59-1797-46ad-860d-6957e4427cab","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"20